data.name: Tatsunecro
data.desc: If this Normal Summoned/Set monster would be used as Synchro Material, 1 monster in your hand can be used as 1 of the other materials. If you do this, all materials for that Summon are banished instead of being sent to the GY. You cannot Special Summon monsters, except Zombie monsters.

card_sets.set_name: Ghosts From the Past: The 2nd Haunting
